; A. Description
;    A list of commands here configures Temperature Sensor module and generates Sensor Clock count/Temperature value
;    through interrupt by Temperature Sensor.
;
; B. Preparation
;    N/A
;
; C. Prerequisite Example (abov_example_config.h)
;    1. TEMP SENSOR
;
; For more information, read a user's manual of the target device carefully.
;
; 1. Channel                      : 0 (TempSens 0)
;
; 2. Config                       : [ 0 i p t ]
;    Operation                    : Interrupt
;    Reference Clock Source       : p (PCLK : Peripheral Clock)
;    Sensor Clock Source          : t (LSITS : Low Speed Internal Temp Sensor Clock)
;
sendln 'cm tempsens'
mpause 30
sendln 'uninit 0'
mpause 30
sendln 'init 0'
mpause 30
sendln 'config 0 i p t'
mpause 30
sendln 'start 0'
